                                        <div class="reviews-summary_summary-bullet-points__YcXK7">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Customers consistently praise exceptional comfort, quick break-in,
                                                    and snug flexible fit enhancing performance</li>
                                                <li>Many highlight striking design, classic tongue return, and bold
                                                    colorways as standout aesthetic features</li>
                                                <li>Reviewers credit cleats with improved ball control, great touch, and
                                                    top-tier quality compared to alternatives</li>
                                                <li>Some mention narrow fit in toebox; material expands with use;
                                                    half-size up recommended for wider feet</li>
                                                <li>A few report isolated quality issues like material stiffness or
                                                    premature wear, though these are rare exceptions</li>
