                                            <div class="reviews-wrapper_review-details__7Gsbx">
                                                <div class="reviews-wrapper_review-title__k3BWC">
                                                    <h4 class="reviews-wrapper_title__ZZa8W">Great boot, but runs small
                                                        in length and width.</h4><span
                                                        class="reviews-wrapper_date__uM0uc">May 25, 2026</span>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="reviews-wrapper_text__mpd_R">The ultimate weapon, but takes
                                                    a little time to set up the fit and wear in. I found the boot runs
                                                    small on length and width so would recommend a half size up, however
                                                    I have experienced some heel lift which can be alleviated somewhat
                                                    with grip socks.</div>
                                                <div class="reviews-wrapper_review-buttons__xdbDI">
                                                    <div class="review-votes_votes__hhvJc"><span
