                                                            class="reviews-wrapper_value__nUXpa">Core Black / Cloud
                                                            White / Lucid Red</span></div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="reviews-wrapper_text__mpd_R">These cleats fit perfectly and
                                                    look even better. Every thing from the feel to the material it’s all
                                                    worth it . Ontop of everything they got delivered earlier than
                                                    expected. Over all they are amazing and so is this brand.</div>
